                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A great Hope fell</l>
                    <l>You heard no <app type="revision"><lem>crash</lem><rdg>crash</rdg></app>
noise</l>
                    <l>The <app type="revision"><lem>havoc</lem><rdg>havoc</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>damage</lem><rdg>damage</rdg></app>
Ruin was within</l>
                    <l>Oh cunning wreck that told no tale</l>
                    <l>And let no Witness in</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The mind was built for mighty Freight</l>
                    <l>For dread occasion planned</l>
                    <l>How often foundering at Sea</l>
                    <l>Ostensibly, on Land</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A not admitting of the wound</l>
                    <l>Until it grew so wide</l>
                    <l>That all my Life had entered it</l>
                    <l>And there were <app type="revision"><lem>space</lem><rdg>space</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>room</lem><rdg>room</rdg></app>
troughs beside</l>
                    <l>_____________</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A closing of the simple lid</l>
                    <l>That opened to the sun</l>
                    <l>Until the tender Carpenter</l>
                    <l>Perpetual nail it down --</l>
